text:
Pros:

- Kindness and responsiveness of the staff;
- size of the room;
- great shower.

(huge) cons:

- way too noisy. I have never experienced such a bad soundproofing in New York. The quality of the windows is not acceptable;
- full light in the room. All blinders have a gap on each of their sides which means that the room is never dark.

Based on the above, it was a huge disappointment and we will definitely not go back at this hotel.
